    "causal_summary": "The single-executor deep-alignment loop dispatches its `cli-codex` leaf with `--sandbox workspace-write` because the leaf is required to Bash-write its three per-iteration artifacts (the iteration narrative, the appended `deep-alignment-state.jsonl` record, and the write-once delta file) — the native `@deep-alignment` agent deliberately has no Write/Edit tool",
